Conway's Game of Life implementation!
Feb. 19th, 2011
jsyang.ca@gmail.com

    The rules of the game; from wikipedia:
        
        Rule    Condition                       Result
        1       LIVE CELL WITH 2,3 NEIGHBORS    LIVES
        2       DEAD CELL WITH 3 NEIGHBORS      LIVES
        3       OTHERWISE, ANY CELL             DIES

canvaslife.html contains a life game that draws on a <canvas>
textlife.html contains a life game that draws in text in a <textarea>
gLayer.js is a custom <canvas> object, includes image loading functionality
and calls back when done.